msgid "# InternVL3.5(InternVL3_5-38B/241B-A28B)"
msgstr "# InternVL3.5（InternVL3_5-38B/241B-A28B）"

msgid "## 1 Introduction"
msgstr "## 1 简介"

msgid ""
"[InternVL3.5](https://huggingface.co/papers/2508.18265), a new family of "
"open-source multimodal models that significantly advances versatility, "
"reasoning capability, and inference efficiency along the InternVL series."
msgstr ""
"[InternVL3.5](https://huggingface.co/papers/2508.18265) 是一个新的开源多模态模型系列，在 "
"InternVL 系列的基础上显著提升了通用性、推理能力和推理效率。"

msgid "The `InternVL3.5` model is first supported in `vllm-ascend:v0.20.2`"
msgstr "`InternVL3.5` 模型在 `vllm-ascend:v0.20.2` 中首次获得支持"

msgid ""
"This document will show the main verification steps of both "
"`InternVL3_5-38B` and `InternVL3_5-241B-A28B` model, including supported "
"features, feature configuration, environment preparation, single-node and "
"multi-node deployment, accuracy and performance evaluation."
msgstr ""
"本文档将展示 `InternVL3_5-38B` 和 `InternVL3_5-241B-A28B` "
"模型的主要验证步骤，包括支持特性、特性配置、环境准备、单节点和多节点部署、精度和性能评估。"

msgid "## 2 Supported Features"
msgstr "## 2 支持的特性"

msgid ""
"Refer to [supported "
"features](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md) to get the "
"model's supported feature matrix."
msgstr ""
"请参考[支持的特性](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md)获取模型支持的特性矩阵。"

msgid ""
"Refer to [feature guide](../../user_guide/feature_guide/index.md) to get the"
" feature's configuration."
msgstr "请参考[特性指南](../../user_guide/feature_guide/index.md)获取特性的配置。"

msgid "## 3 Environment Preparation"
msgstr "## 3 环境准备"

msgid "### 3.1 Model Weight"
msgstr "### 3.1 模型权重"

msgid "require 1 Atlas 800 A3 (64G × 16) node:"
msgstr "需要 1 个 Atlas 800 A3 (64G × 16) 节点："

msgid ""
"- `InternVL3_5-38B-w8a8`: requires 1 Atlas 800 A3 (64G × 16) node [Download model weight](https://modelscope.cn/models/Eco-Tech/InternVL3_5-38B)\n"
"- `InternVL3_5-241B-A28B-w8a8`: requires 1 Atlas 800 A3 (64G × 16) node [Download model weight](https://huggingface.co/OpenGVLab/InternVL3_5-241B-A28B)"
msgstr ""
"- `InternVL3_5-38B-w8a8`：需要 1 个 Atlas 800 A3 (64G × 16) 节点 [下载模型权重](https://modelscope.cn/models/Eco-Tech/InternVL3_5-38B)\n"
"- `InternVL3_5-241B-A28B-w8a8`：需要 1 个 Atlas 800 A3 (64G × 16) 节点 [下载模型权重](https://huggingface.co/OpenGVLab/InternVL3_5-241B-A28B)"

msgid "## 4 Installation"
msgstr "## 4 安装"

msgid "### 4.1 Docker Image Installation"
msgstr "### 4.1 Docker 镜像安装"

msgid "You can use our official docker image to run InternVL3_5 directly."
msgstr "您可以直接使用我们的官方 Docker 镜像来运行 InternVL3_5。"

msgid ""
"To verify the successful installation of the environment, please refer to "
"[installation](../../installation.md)."
msgstr "要验证环境是否安装成功，请参考[安装](../../installation.md)。"

msgid "### 4.2 Source Code Installation"
msgstr "### 4.2 源码安装"

msgid ""
"In addition, if you don't want to use the docker image as above, you can "
"also build all from source:"
msgstr "此外，如果您不想使用上述 Docker 镜像，也可以从源码构建所有内容："

msgid ""
"- Install `vllm-ascend` from source, refer to "
"[installation](../../installation.md)."
msgstr "- 从源码安装 `vllm-ascend`，请参考[安装](../../installation.md)。"

msgid ""
"If you want to deploy multi-node environment, you need to set up environment"
" on each node."
msgstr "如果您想部署多节点环境，需要在每个节点上设置环境。"

msgid "## 5 Online Service Deployment"
msgstr "## 5 在线服务部署"

msgid "### 5.1 Single-Node Online Deployment"
msgstr "### 5.1 单节点在线部署"

msgid "=== \"InternVL3_5-38B\""
msgstr "=== \"InternVL3_5-38B\""

msgid ""
"- Quantized model `InternVL3_5-38B-w8a8` can be deployed on 1 Atlas 800 A3 "
"(64G × 16) ."
msgstr "- 量化模型 `InternVL3_5-38B-w8a8` 可以部署在 1 个 Atlas 800 A3 (64G × 16) 上。"

msgid "=== \"InternVL3_5-241B-A28B\""
msgstr "=== \"InternVL3_5-241B-A28B\""

msgid ""
"- Quantized model `InternVL3_5-241B-A28B-w8a8` can be deployed on 1 Atlas "
"800 A3 (64G × 16) ."
msgstr ""
"- 量化模型 `InternVL3_5-241B-A28B-w8a8` 可以部署在 1 个 Atlas 800 A3 (64G × 16) 上。"

msgid "Run the following script to execute online inference."
msgstr "运行以下脚本执行在线推理。"

msgid ""
"Common Issues Tip: If you encounter issues, Refer to [FAQs](../../faqs.md)."
msgstr "常见问题提示：如果遇到问题，请参考[常见问题解答](../../faqs.md)。"

msgid "**Notice:**"
msgstr "**注意：**"

msgid "Some configurations for optimization are shown below:"
msgstr "一些用于优化的配置如下所示："

msgid ""
"- `VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_FLASHCOMM1`: Enable FlashComm optimization to reduce communication and computation overhead on prefill node. With FlashComm enabled, layer_sharding list cannot include o_proj as an element.\n"
"- `VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_FUSED_MC2`: Enable following fused operators: dispatch_gmm_combine_decode and dispatch_ffn_combine operator."
msgstr ""
"- `VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_FLASHCOMM1`：启用 FlashComm 优化以减少 prefill 节点上的通信和计算开销。启用 FlashComm 后，layer_sharding 列表不能包含 o_proj 作为元素。\n"
"- `VLLM_ASCEND_ENABLE_FUSED_MC2`：启用以下融合算子：dispatch_gmm_combine_decode 和 dispatch_ffn_combine 算子。"

msgid ""
"Please refer to the following python file for further explanation and "
"restrictions of the environment variables above: "
"[envs.py](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-"
"ascend/blob/main/vllm_ascend/envs.py)"
msgstr ""
"有关上述环境变量的进一步解释和限制，请参考以下 Python 文件：[envs.py](https://github.com/vllm-"
"project/vllm-ascend/blob/main/vllm_ascend/envs.py)"

